description:
Danny is breaking down #CountessAndFriends, the Oscars, the #RHONY trailer, and lots more. Special guest QUEENS/ICONS/LEGENDS Michelle Collins (from Sirius XM's The Michelle Collins Show, Edit That Out, and The View) and Lara Marie Schoenhals (host of Babe? and Sexy Unique Podcast) join in on the fun! Plus, there's an important Martha update.
